<%# subject: Welcome to the DB Studio admin portal %>
<div style="<%- S.tagline %>">Admin · Welcome</div>
<h1 style="<%- S.h1 %>">Set up your admin account</h1>
<p style="<%- S.body %>">Hi <%= recipientName %>,</p>
<p style="<%- S.body %>">An admin account has been created for you on the DB Studio portal. Use the link below to set a password, enrol your second factor, and save your backup codes.</p>
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="<%- S.ctaWrap %>">
  <tr><td style="<%- S.ctaCell %>"><a href="<%= welcomeUrl %>" style="<%- S.ctaLink %>">Set up account →</a></td></tr>
</table>
<p style="<%- S.note %>">This invitation expires on <%= euDate(expiresAt) %>. If you weren't expecting it, contact the operator who manages the portal before clicking — admin invitations are issued out-of-band.</p>
